devdoc.details: A simple FIFO queue for storing bytes32 values.

params.item: The bytes32 value to store in the queue.

isEmpty().details: Checks if the queue is empty.

returns._0: True if the queue is empty; otherwise, false.

peek().details: Peeks at the first bytes32 value without removing it.

returns._0: The bytes32 value at the front.

size().details: Returns the size of the queue.

returns._0: The number of elements in the queue.
